API.ADK

Class CANblueConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • API.ADK.CANblueConfiguration

  • public class CANblueConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    Structure for the CANblue configuration. This structure is internally used by the API_ADK for reading the hardware filter list.

    hroesdiyono
